Re creating Flappy Bird
1. Must have a game start screen 
2. Must have endless side scrolling 
3. Must be able to keep score 
4. Must have collision detection 
5. Must have an "end game" screen
6. Must be able to frequently create obstacles
7. Must be able to tap the screen to move vertically 
8. The objects created must be green pipes 
9. Must have some sort gravity that pulls the bird down 
10. Must have sound effects that match the game 
